about:
Inspired by two not so different worlds, Mind Spheres brings you an exclusive and awesome experience. A physics puzzle with minigolf + pinball unique mashup. Figure out puzzles in order to proceed to the next level.
Interactive objects and physics simulations;
50 different maps, difficulty increases every level;
Smooth piano music, relaxing sound design and visuals.

Volunteers fight in a bloody contest for freedom and money. Play as one of three volunteers armed with their favorite weapons, survive waves of enemies and bosses. Red Risk will put you into a bloody tournament, will you survive?
3 players co-op;
Eat, drink and fill your ammo in order to survive;
Elite monsters with unique set of skills to hunt you down.

The Beinbee frog always lived in its swamp and did not interfere with anyone, until it was whirled into a whirlpool and found itself in a closed labyrinth. Help the frog to get out through the almost impassable areas to the frog Beinbee
- light music;
-good graphics;
-simple management;
- interesting gameplay;

Hammerground: Splat! is a virtual reality whack-a-mole-like arcade. 
 Grab a pair of hammers;
 Smash everything that appears in front of you;
 Collect the crystals to extend the countdown timer. 
Hammerground: Splat! features quick play and challange modes. 
This game is designed for Virtual Reality. VR Controllers are required to play Hammerground: Splat!

"Run and Gun" oldschool single-player platformer with NES aesthetics, including an authentic 8-bit chiptune.
Features:
- 10 levels of non-stop action;
- 4 dangerous bosses;
- 2 playable characters with different weapons;
- 7 weapons in total;
